data.description: Certified Preowned Home in Fort Walton Beach! Save yourself time and MONEY with this beautiful home in the heart of Fort Walton Beach. Sellers have just had the home and roof inspected, and are providing the results to the new buyer for FREE! The HVAC has been serviced, and the home is on a monthly pest control maintenance program through Bryan Pest Control. ALL electrical was replaced in 2021 as well! So, you can sleep well at night knowing you may have 99 problems, but your home aint one!Located only 13 minutes to Eglin AFB, 18 minutes to Hurlburt Field, and 10 minutes to the fun and beaches of Okaloosa Island!From an investment standpoint, this home can easily be rented for $2,500/month
